8f87309?u=3D16283549] for lending us her brilliance, to Dan [https://substa=
ck.com/redirect/20daffc9-ea41-4302-8082-f92f997caa71?u=3D16283549] for edit=
ing, and to Conner Swenberg and Mind Apivessa for inspiring thoughts that i=
nformed this piece!
