tage&#8221; and that &#8220;user insight will continue to differentiate con=
sumer apps.&#8221; That seems to be a less durable competitive advantage th=
an the incumbents enjoy.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">In <em><a href=3D"https://substa=
ck.com/redirect/c5a84c0a-b10e-4b6b-a08e-cd61b724940f?u=3D16283549" rel=3D""=
